      "correctAnswer": "Negative weights (but not negative cycles)",
      "explanation": "Floyd's works with negative edge weights but fails if negative weight cycles exist.",
      "difficulty": "medium"
    },
    {
      "id": "mcq-8",
      "question": "The three nested loops in Floyd's algorithm iterate over:",
      "options": [
        {
          "key": "A",
          "text": "Edges, vertices, weights"
        },
        {
          "key": "B",
          "text": "Vertices only"
